  • public class SettingsModelDateBounded
extends org.knime.core.node.defaultnodesettings.SettingsModelLongBounded
    A simple SettingsModel to store only a date (no time) within a bounded range. Supplied dates are normalised to midnight (00:00:00.000) on the supplied day
    Since:
    1.28.0
    Author:
    S.Roughley knime@vernalis.com
